## Development Approach
- Build incrementally - get basic functionality working before adding complexity
- Test as you go - verify each piece works before moving on
- Handle edge cases and error states, not just happy paths
- Make it work, then make it better (avoid premature optimization)
- Provide clear commit messages that explain the "why" not just the "what"

