## Security & Best Practices
- Never hardcode sensitive data (API keys, passwords, secrets)
- Validate and sanitize all user inputs
- Use environment variables for configuration
- Implement proper authentication/authorization where needed
- Follow principle of least privilege

## Performance
- Optimize for readability first, performance second (unless performance is critical)
- Avoid unnecessary re-renders (React) or redundant operations
- Use appropriate data structures and algorithms
- Implement pagination/lazy loading for large datasets
- Profile before optimizing - don't guess at bottlenecks

